{"tid":2399171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫高中仔買兒童卡通內褲XXL碼　家長讚「防學壞」可穿到大學畢業","createTime":"2021-02-08T01:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T02:50:04.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"90c24c30a29b32ab451be768fb2944f99828e293","tid":2399171,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2873330/XXL_thumb_20210207_K_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2873330%2FXXL_thumb_20210207_K_600.jpg&h=f9578b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 台灣一名家長為讀高中的兒子購買兒童內褲XXL碼，還留言大讚可「防止學壞」，會回購。<br />\n<br />\n家長都好擔心子女踏入青春期會學壞，台灣一名家長就有妙計！有男網民日前瀏覽購物網站時，發現有賣家出售兒童內褲，見到其中一個家長留言十分驚嚇，該家長稱買了給高中的兒子穿，滿條圖案卡通的內褲有助防止孩子學壞，還明言會回購，讓兒子穿到大學畢業！<br />\n<br />\n一名男網民在網上討論區「Dcard」發帖文分享稱，他在一購物網站上看到有賣家出售男童內褲，3款都有藍色花紋圖案，看來精美可愛，每條僅售50台幣（約14港元），且獲得4.9星（5星滿分）超高評價，可見質素好，深受家長歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2873330/underwear_01a_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2873330%2Funderwear_01a_600.jpg&h=2d109558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網站出售的男童內褲款式。（Dcard圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2873330/underwear_01b_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2873330%2Funderwear_01b_600.jpg&h=5a8e47a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每條只售50台幣（約14港元），一共3款。（Dcard圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2873330/underwear_02a_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2873330%2Funderwear_02a_600.jpg&h=90daf996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有家長留言是買給高中的兒子穿著，還表示會回購，讓兒子穿到大學畢業。（Dcard圖片）<br />\n<br />\n卡通圖案能防止小孩學壞<br />\n男網民發現其中一個留言有亮點，是一名家長買入了其中一款「暖藍色、XXL碼」的內褲，留下5星正評，並留言稱是買給讀高中的兒子穿。<br />\n&ldquo;有滿版的卡通圖案很不錯，能防止小孩學壞，預計讓小孩穿到大學畢業，還會再回購～&rdquo;<br />\n留言令男網民爆笑，擔心其兒子穿上會覺到逼狹，還要穿到大學畢業，驚歎該名家長的家教「應該是不得了」！<br />\n<br />\n網民同情︰孩子一定活得很辛苦<br />\n帖文令網民爆笑，「防止孩子學壞笑死」，但也想像到該名孩子一定被控制得很辛苦。"},{"pid":"4a6fd2c3f79ecf03ebf811172e9eecc1dfbb56d7","tid":2399171,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"同女扑野比女女睇到都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b83e81c0a355facff340d9262345d69176368f","tid":2399171,"uid":238920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"第時阿仔大個唔好問做咩仲未有女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79de839651dcae69bb2634dfe3eb6d5a75eacec6","tid":2399171,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除庫準備同女同學做愛嘅時候比人笑"},{"pid":"b6441c3e43b6f4c26bf6b2ebca00b58d14e4d6da","tid":2399171,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T01:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ae77f9c7c9f6ca3778e351957bbb8c627fc405","tid":2399171,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"想個仔做魔法師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f473f8d9f0310cc55d81c19776db2afe5a51a8","tid":2399171,"uid":157439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"到要扑嘢果陣就會買底褲換㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab6786580d5c4e8b9e484120e4c59e32753eeca","tid":2399171,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"新情趣，好似同細路女搞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7114e44424aeca94af4d7587e7901a543568849","tid":2399171,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"台灣咁多「媽寶」應該會乖乖地聽啊媽話著到大學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}